Evidence for somatostatin-like immunoreactivity in discrete cells of the 
anterior pituitary of camel (Camelus dromedarius).

Quéré M, el May A, Bouzakoura C, Dubois MP, Dubois PM.

Immunocytochemical methods were applied to camel pituitaries. ACTH, 
beta-lipotropin (LPH), LH beta, GH, TSH, and PRL immunoreactive cells were 
identified. They were located on different parts of anterior pituitary and had 
different organization and shape. In addition, somatostatin-like 
